These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, dutch, russian, japanese
4 different pets are kept: turtle, bird, hedgehog, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the colombian##1
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the russian##3
4. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
5. the japanese is not to the left of the owner of the mouse##8
6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
7. the dutch is somewhere between the colombian and the owner of the bird##7
8. the dutch and the owner of the mouse have the same parity positions##9
9. the russian and the owner of the turtle have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch | russian     | japanese |
| Pet           | hedgehog   | mouse     | bird | turtle  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, soy-milk, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, board-games, video-games, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is hiking and the person drinking juice have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
6. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
7. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda     | soy-milk    | water | juice    |
| Hobby      | card-games | board-games | video-games      | hiking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, soy-milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: tomato, pear, pineapple, raspberry
1. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
2. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
7. the person eating tomato is not to the left of the person eating pear##8
8. the person drinking almond-milk and the person eating pear have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | soy-milk   | sprite    | tea  |
| Food       | pear | raspberry | tomato | pineapple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, electrician, dancer, scientist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, ambient, classical, rock
1. the fan techno is the electrician##1
2. the fan ambient is on the right of the fan classical##1
3. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the electrician##5
4. the fan rock is on the left or right of the dancer##3
5. the fan ambient is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the scientist and the fan rock have the same parity positions##9
7. the dancer is on the left or right of the engineer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | scientist | dancer | engineer  | electrician |
| Music-Genre   | classical             | ambient          | rock | techno    |

