2. the owner of the mouse and the fan metal have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the lizard and the fan funk have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the fan pop##5
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the fan indie##1
6. the fan funk is not the owner of the lizard##6
7. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the fan funk##5
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the fan metal##1
9. the owner of the rabbit is not the fan indie##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal | pop | indie  | funk |
| Pet           | lizard   | mouse     | fish | rabbit      |

