6. the russian is not to the left of the person watching western movies##8
7. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
8. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the argentine##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
