2. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
3. the person who's sport is rugby and the fan blues have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the fan blues is not to the right of the fan reggae##8
6. the fan pop is somewhere to the left of the fan reggae##5
7. the fan blues is somewhere to the right of the fan techno##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | pop | blues         | reggae     |
| Sport         | surfing | rugby  | water-polo | cycling |

