2. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is not the owner of the frog##6
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
7. the person who's hobby is dancing and the owner of the cat have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | dancing | camping | traveling | hiking |
| Pet     | goldfish     | pony     | cat     | frog    |

