2. the egyptian is not to the right of the japanese##8
3. the person eating apple is not to the left of the person eating banana##8
4. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
5. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the spanish##3
6. the egyptian is on the far left##1
7. the japanese is on the left of the person eating apple##1
8. the person eating apricot is the thai##1
9. the person eating banana and the japanese have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | kale   | banana    | apple | apricot    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | japanese | spanish   | thai |

