The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, scientific, time-travel, sports
1. the person watching thriller movies is not the person drinking milk##6
2. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
8. the person watching thriller movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching time-travel movies and the person drinking juice have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | milk   | soy-milk  | juice  | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | time-travel | sports | thriller      |

