.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, coffee, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, indie, electronic, house
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan electronic have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 3. the fan techno is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking tea##7
 4. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 5. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan electronic is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
 7. the person drinking sprite and the fan indie have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the fan house##3
 9. the fan house is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the fan techno##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea  | sprite | coffee  | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | house | electronic     | techno | indie     |

