.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, sprite, lemonade
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, chess, woodworking, baking
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 6. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 7. the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is chess have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is chess have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | sprite        | lemonade   | 7up      |
| Hobby      | baking | woodworking | chess | writing |

 